---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="About"
  description="PDX Events is a curated collection of Portland event calendars, favorites, and pickup soccer resources — built by Ian Rosado."
  pageClass="page-events"
>
  <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">

    <header class="mb-10">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-semibold text-stone-900 mb-3" style="font-family: var(--font-serif)">About PDX Events</h1>
      <p class="text-stone-500 text-lg">A personal project by a Portlander who wanted all the good stuff in one place.</p>
    </header>

    <section class="mb-8 bg-white rounded-2xl border border-stone-100 shadow-sm p-6">
      <h2 class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-orange-600 mb-3">What is this?</h2>
      <p class="text-stone-600 leading-relaxed mb-3">
        PDX Events is a curated set of Google Calendars, maps, and resources for things happening around Portland, Oregon.
        It covers local events and staples, farmers markets, trivia nights by neighborhood, Pedalpalooza rides, pickup soccer games, and favorite spots around the city.
      </p>
      <p class="text-stone-600 leading-relaxed">
        Everything here is hand-curated — no algorithms, no ads, no sponsored content. Just things I've found useful after 10+ years of living in Portland.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8 bg-white rounded-2xl border border-stone-100 shadow-sm p-6">
      <h2 class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-orange-600 mb-3">Who made it?</h2>
      <p class="text-stone-600 leading-relaxed mb-3">
        I'm Ian Rosado — a data and analytics engineer based in Portland, OR. I've lived here for over 10 years and built this site because I kept getting asked by friends and newcomers: <em>"How do I find out what's going on in Portland?"</em>
      </p>
      <p class="text-stone-600 leading-relaxed">
        PDX Events is one part of my personal site. If you want to know more about me, see my recipes, or read about my travels, visit
        <a href="https://www.ianrosado.com" class="text-orange-600 hover:text-orange-700 underline underline-offset-2 font-medium">ianrosado.com</a>.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="bg-white rounded-2xl border border-stone-100 shadow-sm p-6">
      <h2 class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-orange-600 mb-3">Something missing?</h2>
      <p class="text-stone-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
        Know of an event, calendar, game, or spot I should add? Use the suggestion form on any of the calendar pages — I read every submission.
      </p>
      <a
        href="/"
        class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-orange-600 hover:bg-orange-700 text-white text-sm font-semibold px-5 py-2.5 rounded-xl transition-colors"
      >
        Browse the calendars
      </a>
    </section>

  </div>
</Layout>
